<br>
Those are really fun quests IMO and should be implented more. Like a troll quest vs the inhabitants of guk. You and your troll buddies go and initiate the quest and help some troll mercinaries lay seige to guk. You can do this with practically every zone in the game, but It wouldn't be fun then.<br>
<br>
Just rambling now hehe. Hope to see some fun quests that don't involve camping or waiting for a rare spawn/item to get a crappy reward. <p>Binnamar- 51 dwarven warrior<BR>
